 <notes>
New bindings have been added.

Detached signatures:
* crypto_sign_detached() computes a signature and returns it without a
copy of the initial message
* crypto_sign_verify_detached() verifies that a signature matches a
given message.

Authenticated encryption with additional data (chacha20poly1305):
* crypto_aead_chacha20poly1305_encrypt()
* crypto_aead_chacha20poly1305_decrypt()

Stream cipher (salsa20):
* Sodium::crypto_stream()
* Sodium::crypto_stream_xor()

Constant-time bin/hex conversions:
* Sodium::sodium_bin2hex()
* Sodium::sodium_hex2bin()
 </notes>
